Home Alone 2: Lost in New York;;62;;35;;PG;;After snarky youth Kevin McCallister (Macaulay Culkin) loses track of his father at the airport, he mistakenly gets on a plane headed for New York City -- while the rest of the McCallisters fly to Florida. Now alone in the Big Apple, Kevin cons his way into a room at the Plaza Hotel and begins his usual antics. But when Kevin discovers that the Sticky Bandits (Joe Pesci, Daniel Stern) are on the loose, he struggles to stop them from robbing an elderly man's toy store just before Christmas.;;Other,Comedy,Kids & family;;Chris Columbus;;1992;;Macaulay Culkin,Joe Pesci,Daniel Stern,Catherine O'Hara,John Heard,Devin Ratray,Tim Curry,Brenda Fricker,Eddie Bracken,Gerry Bamman,Kieran Culkin,Rob Schneider,Bob Eubanks,Ally Sheedy,Ron Canada;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/home_alone_2_lost_in_new_york